The active improvement roadmap is maintained in IMPROVEMENTS.md at the
repository root. Each numbered phase there is independently mergeable
and carries its own scope / acceptance notes.

High-level buckets currently pending:

  * Charset handling (UTF-8 -> Latin-1 transliteration)
  * CSS subset (inline style + <style> blocks)
  * picture.datatype fallback for WebP / SVG / AVIF
  * Parser bugs: body-less text, entities without ;, FS dither tile seams
  * Headless rendering regression tests in CI
  * Memory-safety pass (ASan + fuzzing)
  * gzip Content-Encoding
  * Cookie jar hook (opt-in)
  * target="_blank" notification

See IMPROVEMENTS.md for the full list.
